<title>USA: Air Methods board OKs 5 pct shr buyback.</title>
<headline>Air Methods board OKs 5 pct shr buyback.</headline>
<dateline>DENVER 1996-12-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Air Methods Corp said Thursday it authorized a stock repurchase plan to buy back up to five percent of the outstanding shares of the company's common stock.</p>
<p>The repurchase will be funded from existing cash balances, and the repurchased shares will be retired, the company said.</p>
